{"tid":922782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［請輸入名稱］殯儀館看更的故事","createTime":"2018-11-30T16:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T13:53:11.000Z","uid":185416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbd291ac9277d1323a9a960417fc5cfd2a10e54","tid":922782,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"所有選項以最多正評者為準<br />\n呢個係一個恐怖懸疑故事<br />\n<br />\n==開始==<br />\n<br />\n中五畢業，打咗幾年散工，搵得雞碎咁多，經過一輪掙扎之後，叫朋友介紹我入去殯儀館做看更。<br />\n返中午放凌晨，人工$45,000，即簽約翌日返工。<br />\n<br />\n聽日係我第一日返工，老細同我講聽日會做一單謀殺案死者嘅生意<br />\n<br />\n1）準備扮病唔返工<br />\n2）今晚早啲訓，聽日養足精神返工<br />\n3）上網睇下發生咩事先再決定<br />\n<br />\n現有物品：十字架"},{"pid":"753e916a8b35b4ad23a3631592b7f98b24358f24","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5c871b86de72b8324d3f3337e315277db8ec39d9","tid":922782,"uid":39734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2847b35b172d3158e8014cdc03fdba648765b272","tid":922782,"uid":185416,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"753e916a8b35b4ad23a3631592b7f98b24358f24","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:08:57.000Z","msg":"2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"啪啪！啪啪！<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企<br />\n老竇喺廚房切緊肉，準備緊今日嘅飯菜<br />\n我一路睇電視，廚房一直傳來切肉嘅聲音<br />\n持續左半個鐘，一直都冇停過<br />\n我大鬧：［搞乜撚嘢咁耐都未切完㗎！］<br />\n<br />\n正當我準備行入廚房屌柒佢嘅時候<br />\n我偷睇到.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQ23d0H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQ23d0H.gif&h=38dee350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢不斷咁切緊自己隻腳！！！<br />\n<br />\n1）即刻掉頭走<br />\n2）即刻阻止佢<br />\n3）報警"},{"pid":"2001818e2824d0a31508dc816e7c352a3eba706f","tid":922782,"uid":9464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ed92c6e9142269644f1f80656024a703f6bbb5c1","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d612ad93bb3ae7317ea7f8e2f4241e1c30247729","tid":922782,"uid":185416,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed92c6e9142269644f1f80656024a703f6bbb5c1","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"［哇屌！］我嚇到大叫左出聲<br />\n我乜都唔撚理，直接調轉頭沖入廁所<br />\n當我回過神來，望一望快鏡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我個樣變咗一個女人㗎！<br />\n我都未講得切諗發生咩事嘅時候，老竇喺門外面不斷咁撞門話：［就嚟食得飯啦，我煮左你最鍾意食嘅嘢俾你...］<br />\n與此同時，鏡入面我嘅樣不斷咁變化<br />\n<br />\n未久，門終於受唔住力，比我老竇撞開咗<br />\n［你最鍾意嘅人肉湯到啦.....］<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩！！！！！！！！！<br />\n喺夢入邊扎醒左嘅我，清楚咁記得老竇同埋個女係咩樣<br />\n我坐喺床上面，成晚都冷靜唔到<br />\n<br />\n仆街，早知唔咁早瞓<br />\n<br />\n1）準備定聽日返工嘅嘢<br />\n2）瞓返<br />\n3）準備定聽日請假<br />\n4）去叫雞定下驚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ndJYy3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ndJYy3.png&h=feb3da7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf2bb62319dff664eaed32303e552f54f8d0ab08","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"60205f1d38c7ce96287f7ab8329622587aee456c","tid":922782,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf2bb62319dff664eaed32303e552f54f8d0ab08","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"4"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"反應好先再寫"},{"pid":"9fe815491e95a4056acad380e543d50bb8e270d3","tid":922782,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf2bb62319dff664eaed32303e552f54f8d0ab08","tid":922782,"uid":7824,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy